OL,3,CMP urges Prime Minister to define
OL,4,CIslamophobia to drive 'vitriol' off
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FThe Government should define
OL,8,FIslamophobia to combat "the racism and
OL,9,Fvitriol we are seeing by a minority of
OL,10,Ffar-right activists on Britain's
OL,11,Fstreets", a Labour MP has said.
OL,13,FAfzal Khan, who represents Manchester
OL,14,FRusholme, has written to Prime
OL,15,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer, urging him
OL,16,Fto host meetings with Muslim community
OL,17,Fleaders and to formally adopt a
OL,18,Fdefinition of anti-Muslim prejudice
OL,19,Fput forward by the All-Party
OL,20,FParliamentary Group (APPG) on British
OL,21,FMuslims.
