OL,3,CMP urges Prime Minister to define
OL,4,CIslamophobia to drive 'vitriol' off
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FIt follows almost a week of violent
OL,8,Fdisorder in towns and cities in parts
OL,9,Fof the UK, after stabbings in
OL,10,FSouthport, which both Sir Keir and
OL,11,FConservative former home secretary
OL,12,FDame Priti Patel have described as
OL,13,F"thuggery".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@JO]
