OL,3,CMP urges Prime Minister to define
OL,4,CIslamophobia to drive 'vitriol' off
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FMr Khan, who was named the first
OL,8,FMuslim Lord Mayor of Manchester 19
OL,9,Fyears ago before becoming an MP,
OL,10,Fwrote: "This violence has been stoked
OL,11,Fby the far-right and fuelled by
OL,12,Fwidespread Islamophobia which have
OL,13,Fbecome mainstream over the past 14
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,F"I welcome the strong leadership you
OL,17,Fand your cabinet have shown on this
OL,18,Fissue, rejecting the classification of
OL,19,Fthis rioting as legitimate protests,
OL,20,Fand convening an urgent Cobra meeting
OL,21,Fthis morning (Monday)."
OL,26,@rD@HOU}D@WO]
