OL,3,CMP urges Prime Minister to define
OL,4,CIslamophobia to drive 'vitriol' off
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FMr Khan added: "It is imperative that
OL,8,Fthis Labour Government, in stark
OL,9,Fcontrast to the previous Conservative
OL,10,Fgovernments, will not ignore
OL,11,FIslamophobia when it occurs."
OL,13,FHe urged the prime minister to meet
OL,14,Fregional Muslim leaders "particularly
OL,15,Fin areas where the violence has been
OL,16,Fconcentrated", and to brief them on
OL,17,Fwhat action is being taken to de-
OL,18,Fescalate tension.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@]O]
