OL,3,CMP urges Prime Minister to define
OL,4,CIslamophobia to drive 'vitriol' off
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FMr Khan also pointed to the APPG's
OL,8,Fdefinition of Islamophobia, produced
OL,9,Fafter a 2017 inquiry, which reads:
OL,10,F"Islamophobia is rooted in racism and
OL,11,Fis a type of racism that targets
OL,12,Fexpressions of Muslimness or perceived
OL,13,FMuslimness."
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@LO]
