OL,7,FA spokesman for then-prime minister
OL,8,FRishi Sunak said in February the
OL,9,Fproposed wording "conflates race with
OL,10,Freligion, does not address
OL,11,Fsectarianism within Islam, and may
OL,12,Funintentionally undermine freedom of
OL,13,Fspeech".
OL,15,FHe added: "We have always been clear
OL,16,Fthat this government does not and will
OL,17,Fnot tolerate anti-Muslim hatred."
