OL,7,FLabour has included the definition in
OL,8,Fits own Islamophobia Policy ` the
OL,9,Fparty's document which bans its
OL,10,Factivists from "acts of
OL,11,Fdiscrimination, prejudice or hostility
OL,12,Fbased on religion or race".
OL,14,FThe Government has pledged to bolster
OL,15,Fa #29.4 million Protective Security
OL,16,Ffor Mosques Scheme, with funding for
OL,17,Fsecurity at religious venues and
OL,18,Fschools.
