OL,7,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said: "In
OL,8,Flight of the disgraceful threats and
OL,9,Fattacks that local mosques have also
OL,10,Ffaced in many communities, the
OL,11,FGovernment is providing rapid
OL,12,Fadditional support through the
OL,13,FProtective Security for Mosques
OL,14,FScheme, alongside the support from
OL,15,Flocal police forces and we repeat that
OL,16,Fanyone involved in this disorder and
OL,17,Fviolence will face the full force of
OL,18,Fthe law."
